data.text: Lilian Velez Story, till death do us part is a 1995 Tagalog-language Biography Crime motion picture written by Tony Calvento and Carlo J. Caparas. The movie is directed by Carlo J. Caparas. Sharon Cuneta plays the biographical account of the murder case of Filipina movie actress Lilian Velez during the 1950's. Lilian velez story, till death do us part stars Sharon Cuneta, Cesar Montano, Joel Torre, Shannen Torres, Gina Alajar, Donita Rose and Soraya. It was released on 8th February 1995.
